{"tid":104071,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"第二屆屍骨ANGEL緣份計劃","createTime":"2017-02-01T19:55:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T09:57:18.000Z","uid":80364,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3971b37cc99a471c5fe7e1f0ec9427cf2ca26227","tid":104071,"uid":80364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T19:55:28.000Z","msg":"回顧15年聖誕小弟係HKG搞左個屍骨天使緣份計劃<br />\n巴絲既表現都尚算湧躍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舊LINK:<br />\n<a href=\"http://archive.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6157497&amp;page=1&amp;highlight_id=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.hkgolden.com%2Fview.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6157497%26page%3D1%26highlight_id%3D0&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e712add2\" target=\"_blank\">http://archive.hkgolden.com/view.aspx?message=6157497&amp;page=1&amp;highlight_id=0</a><br />\n最後活動有10巴10絲出黎, 總算冇搞串個場<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要多謝上年有個參加既巴打好樂力咁比氣氛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開頭個場好似比我搞DEAD左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩年後重出江湖決定趁毒撚節前搞多次比大家玩<br />\n唔多講, 規則如下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 參加者認真提交表格所需填妥內容, 以作配對secret angel 配對之用 <br />\n<br />\n參加者在表格中自訂一個花名(葉瘤 / 肥西老母雞 / 戰神)etc...<br />\n<br />\n2. 配對結果為一對一. 結果將會以wechat/whatsapp 送出. 配對結果將會以亞視六合彩抽籤方式進行. 10/2 成功被選中既巴絲將會收到信息通知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 於活動期間11-17號, 你將會有幾日既時間以whatsapp了解你既屍骨Angel, 為保持神秘性,期間不可交換facebook, 見面, 同埋要轉走有你個樣既頭像.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 成功入選既朋友將會被加入一個Group, 只用作群聊, 大會公告之用. 私聊是禁止的.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5. 為促進遊戲進行, 大台每2日都會有一個小任務比參加者去完成. 請大家積極參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完結日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <br />\n<br />\n6.活動完既日子 如反應熱烈, 暫定17/2 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 將會有一個小活動 [尋找對方的屍骨] - (交換聖誕禮物, /聚餐, / Cafe) 比大家見你既屍骨Angel <br />\n活動後屍骨Angel 亦可以回復自由身, 不受遊戲限制 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS1: - MK同5p呃蝦條<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- 遊戲間請彼此尊重 <br />\n- 如對方有過火行為, 請向大會報告, 後補名單將會替上 <br />\n<br />\nPS2: 切勿隨意透露任何重要/個人資料。 <br />\n<br />\nPSP: 請遵守遊戲規則, 包括隱藏自己既身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nPSP: 是次活動資料只會用於本活動之用. 並不會公開, 外洩, 其他用途 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎巴絲提供意見令活動更加完善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n報名表格:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdajvHxW6O08L-n02G4r23AVzj8AIGvPIiUKp-B58qzO_tNlg/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdajvHxW6O08L-n02G4r23AVzj8AIGvPIiUKp-B58qzO_tNlg%2Fviewform&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=f3bac4ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdajvHxW6O08L-n02G4r23AVzj8AIGvPIiUKp-B58qzO_tNlg/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a14b2ffe5ece87c9e00c3317e0ed2af3de4031","tid":104071,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T04:33:32.000Z","msg":"咩屍骨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a85019edefbfb67a068110b9b43a6d871de667d8","tid":104071,"uid":56763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:29:03.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下上年搞成點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d431423565a1fe07ca39767f39d4a3f371df9317","tid":104071,"uid":40499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T05:48:45.000Z","msg":"比活動既相睇下"},{"pid":"49bba9e935e0bed4b3aa2597ae321df8bba71b04","tid":104071,"uid":80364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-02T11:02:31.000Z","msg":"Secret angel呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f125d69ec02da2c36f79780fe011b6ed44c5c2c","tid":104071,"uid":4323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T14:39:16.000Z","msg":"有咩小任務"},{"pid":"5cb074db1e57eaa45a4e08d8ca5cc734b9e9f48d","tid":104071,"uid":56763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T09:57:18.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小妹今年讀緊大學，之前係到都試過搞一次party，因為想再練習下自己搞event同做Mc嘅技巧，依家得到幾位朋友既幫忙，肯幫手做搞手，但唯一係差左出席活動既巴絲打 <br />\n<br />\n所以上黎問問，有冇巴絲打願意出席今次活動 <br />\n<br />\n我會book場，已經揀定咗幾間， <br />\n可能會係book party room之後叫到會， <br />\n又或者BBQ <br />\n<br />\n會有啲小遊戲同大家玩吓咁 <br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇巴絲打有興趣 <br />\n<br />\n時間：暫定9月24日（星期日）夜晚 <br />\n名額：巴打8位，絲打8位 <br />\n地點：TBC (多數九龍旺區） <br />\n費用： <br />\n巴打250 <br />\n絲打100 <br />\n（包場同包食)<br />\n<br />\n利申: 冇賺任何錢，只求唔蝕同唔好嫌棄我冇咩經驗 <br />\n同希望巴絲打玩完後可以比返feedback <br />\n<br />\n有意就填下面張google form啦 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScgWBdH7DJuf28FLIhWImS3aW9ss0HrYHjByN8Nr1ggaDrk5g/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScgWBdH7DJuf28FLIhWImS3aW9ss0HrYHjByN8Nr1ggaDrk5g%2Fviewform&d=HVFDXqn9keSrFxh6Mt7Td3Iou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=747191b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScgWBdH7DJuf28FLIhWImS3aW9ss0HrYHjByN8Nr1ggaDrk5g/viewform</a>"}]}